\f0\b \cf0 Links
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\ri0\sl312\slmult1

\f0 \cf0 ____ Add bluehornet/icontact codes for links to view online, unsubscribe, forward to a friend, etc.
\f1 \

\f0 ____ Add all other links given by client such as social media, link to homepage, etc. 
\f1 \

\f0 ____ Add fake links when necessary <a href=\'94#\'94> like around image buttons. Then ASK CLIENT if you do not know the link to use.
\f2 \uc0\u8232 
\f1 \
\pard\tx0\pardeftab720\sl312\slmult1

\f0\b \cf0 Styles 
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\ri0\sl312\slmult1

\f0 \cf0 ____ Write out hex colors with 6 characters instead of shorthand (3) #000000
\f1 \

\f0 ____ Customize link and text colors in <head> styles and <body> tag
\f1 \

\f0 ____ Add font-family, font-size, line-height, and color to \cf3 every cell that contains text\cf0 !
\f1 \

\f0 ____ Fix addresses/numbers (like in footer) from showing up as links on iPhones by wrapping in a span with the ioslinks class. Customize the ioslinks class to be the desired text color.
\f1 \
\
\pard\tx0\pardeftab720\sl312\slmult1
