\f0\b \cf0 If BlueHornet [all HighRoad clients]
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx0\pardeftab720\sl312\slmult1

\f0\b \cf4 Do not use meta tags. 
\b0 \cf0 Meta tags are stripped out by default by BlueHornet and can sometimes cause the entire head/styles to be removed as well. Instead just use our starter template which works well with that system.
